&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Data Analyst&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and update innovation portfolio data across systems and tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure data accuracy, completeness, and consistency through regular audits and clean-up activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support teams in entering and updating project data, acting as a go-to resource for questions and troubleshooting&lt;/li&gt;
